### Save a new Todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Todo 4",
  "isCompleted": true
}

### Get all Todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos

### Get a todo by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/1

### Update todo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/todos/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Todo 3",
  "isCompleted": false
}

### Delete a todo
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/todos/4
